{"id":"1sapu64","title":"From Small Caps to ~$40K Profit — Not Huge, But a Milestone for Me","author":"Zealousideal-Hat4801","created_utc":1775155190,"score":23,"selftext":"Not a massive account compared to many here but this is a milestone I’m genuinely proud of\n\nI’ve been focusing mainly on small caps and short-term momentum plays Over time I realized consistency matters way more than chasing big wins\n\nThis \\~$40K didn’t come from one trade   it was built gradually through:\n\nCutting losses quicker than before\n\nLetting winners run a bit longer\n\nAvoiding overtrading (still working on this)\n\nSticking to setups instead of emotions\n\nI’m not claiming any edge or perfection  just sharing progress. Still learning every day\n\nMy friend and I compiled a set of strategies and methods for analyzing market trends and shared them in the group If you are interested please leave a comment or contact me directly Hopefully this will help those who can truly benefit from this guidance","url":"https://i.redd.it/31xyjueumtsg1.png","comments":[{"id":"odxn2k7","author":"Few_File_5974","body":"Are you willing to share it with me? I'm interested","score":1,"created_utc":1775156017,"is_op":false,"replies":[{"id":"odxn7t0","author":"Zealousideal-Hat4801","body":"Of course you can","score":1,"created_utc":1775156057,"is_op":true,"replies":[]},{"id":"oe1auw3","author":"Expensive-Badger-142","body":"Hey mate how’s it going ? What do you use for your TA? ","score":1,"created_utc":1775204229,"is_op":false,"replies":[]}]},{"id":"odxrclg","author":"Independent-Tea-1667","body":"I'm interested","score":1,"created_utc":1775157215,"is_op":false,"replies":[{"id":"odxrph9","author":"Zealousideal-Hat4801","body":"send","score":1,"created_utc":1775157318,"is_op":true,"replies":[]}]},{"id":"odxul3v","author":"YourBr0ther","body":"I'm interested\n\n","score":1,"created_utc":1775158139,"is_op":false,"replies":[{"id":"odxv4d9","author":"Zealousideal-Hat4801","body":"Please check your messages